Package it.polimi.ingsw.common.messages.responses

Class SharedGameState

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.common.messages.responses.SharedGameState
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SharedGameState extends Object implements Serializable
This class holds a representation of the current state of the game relative to a particular player. This class is used as a virtual-view for all players inside a game
